[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] ## 3. Type: Short Answer
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.774Z] [INFO] [stderr] | 2 | Seminars are longer than lectures. | True (0) |
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] A question is posed that requires a short written answer, typically 1–3 words or a number. The answer must be extracted verbatim (or acceptably paraphrased) from the recording.
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] ### Format
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] ### Data Structure (compatible with `ListeningQuestion`)
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] | 6 | The library is open 24 hours on weekends during exam periods. | Not Given (2) |
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] {
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] ---
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr]   question: string          // The question (e.g., "What time does the direct flight depart?")
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr]   id: string
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr]   type: 'short-answer'
