[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] > Note: For full compatibility with the current `ListeningQuestion` interface (without adding `acceptableAnswers`), use `blanks: [correctAnswer]` and consider the blank field as the answer container. The UI renderer would interpret `short-answer` similarly to `gap-fill` but with a single free-text input.
