[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] ## 4. Type: Multiple Answer
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] A question is presented with a list of options. The candidate must select **all** correct answers (commonly 2 or 3 out of 5–7 options). This is distinct from `multiple-choice` where exactly one option is correct.
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] ### Data Structure (compatible with `ListeningQuestion` — with `correctAnswer` as `string` using comma-separated indices)
[2026-07-04T06:05:51.775Z] [INFO] [stderr] ```typescript
